---
description: Quality and testing requirements
globs:
  - "**/*test*"
  - "**/tests/**"
  - "**/*.spec.*"
alwaysApply: false
---

Prefer behavior-focused tests over implementation snapshots.

Release-blocking areas:
- cross-tenant access;
- webhook verification and replay;
- idempotency;
- PII redaction;
- AI evidence validation;
- migrations;
- deletion;
- backup restore;
- official provider contract behavior.

External provider calls are mocked or use explicit sandbox opt-in.
Never allow tests to call paid APIs by default.
